4ï¸âƒ£ OR query
db.students.find({ $or: [ { course: "CS" }, { marks: { $lt: 80 } } ] })

5ï¸âƒ£ NOT query
db.students.find({ marks: { $not: { $gt: 90 } } })

6ï¸âƒ£ Querying for Null
db.students.insertOne({ name: "Kiran", course: null })
db.students.find({ course: null })

7ï¸âƒ£ Regular Expression query
